{"id": "art-244", "label": "Art. 244", "title": "Art. 244: Terminarea cercetării procesului", "slug": "art-244", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_407511271\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1283\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_407511271\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 244:\nTerminarea cercet&#259;rii procesului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1876288141\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1282\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1876288141\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Când judec&#259;torul se socote&#351;te l&#259;murit,\ndeclar&#259; cercetarea procesului încheiat&#259; &#351;i poate fixa un alt\ntermen pentru dezbaterea fondului, din oficiu sau la cererea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1064276204\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1281\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1064276204\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul în care s-a dispus dezbaterea fondului la un\nalt termen, judec&#259;torul poate pune în vedere p&#259;r&#355;ilor s&#259;\nredacteze note privind sus&#355;inerile lor &#351;i s&#259; le depun&#259; la\ndosar cu cel pu&#355;in 5 zile înainte de termenul stabilit potrivit alin. (1),\nf&#259;r&#259; a aduce atingere dreptului acestora de a formula concluzii\norale.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Excep&#355;iile\nprocesuale</span></b></p>"}